dialogue: After running for a long while, Spirit finally
manages to get away from the soldiers.
*pant, pant* Finally got them off my tail *pant*
*pant* hope those two made it away
But now how am I gonna find that guy again now...
As she was trying to make a plan, she meets eyes
with the very person she was looking for.
*pant* Well, if it isn't my savior in sweaty armor.
You're not much better yourself.
What can you do? Anyway I haven't gotten around to
thanking you for your help yet, have I? Thanks, a lot.
Why'd you go and piss them off so much anyway?
Oh, nothing much. Just noticed them trying to bully
rations out of a child. I couldn't
just sit there, doing nothing.
What?!
Yeah, didn't realize those Empire sickos could get any worse either.
Anyway, I wanted to thank you. If ya ever need a favor
'round here, know you can call on Whisk.
Well actually, I have a package to deliver.
From the description the client gave, it seems like its for you.
Mind taking it off my hands?
Wait a...you're the courier? Yes! Thank you so much!
Woah, easy.
Oh, sorry, sorry. It's just, it'll be so helpful,
having these supplies. They can help a lot of people...
...What type of supplies are they exactly?
Come on, let's take it back to camp and I'll show you.
